E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1305','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-13/70a747939d1b691ff470906d500886f0.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">在官桥镇检查指导塘堰整修工作<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-13/9f93f744d4a1708c41edf4558e3c3efd.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n在潘家湾镇检查指导沟渠清挖工作</span>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>日，省纪委常委、秘书长李昌海一行来我县检查指导&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作，县委书记熊征宇，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，县委常委、副县长许标，副县长魏萍陪同检查。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">检查组一行先后深入到官桥镇官桥村、朱砂村，潘家湾镇四邑村、畈湖村等地，详细听取了镇村干部关于&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作的情况汇报，并就各地塘堰整治和沟渠清挖的资金筹措及到位情况、帮扶单位工作开展情况，工程进展及完工时间等进行详细的了解和记录。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇表示，下一阶段，我县将紧扣&ldquo;挖塘堰、强基础、惠民生&rdquo;的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动主题，以&ldquo;转作风、办实事、促发展&rdquo;为目标，坚持把&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动作为巩固执政基础的政治大事、保障群众利益的民生大事、促进农村发展的全局大事来对待、部署和落实，进一步加强领导、精心组织，确保&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动取得明显成效。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">通过看现场、听汇报、查资料等方式，检查组一致认为，我县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展得非常扎实，进展顺利、成效显著，切实为农民解了难事，办了实事。检查组要求我县全面完成在建工程的煞尾工作，为及时有效地发挥沟渠塘堰的灌溉排涝作用打下坚实的基础。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">据介绍，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展以来，我县超前谋划、精心组织，共组建<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">103</span>个工作队、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">350</span>余名机关干部深入全县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">82</span>个行政村、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">513</span>个村民小组，掀起了全县新一轮&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的高潮。截至目前，全县已完成塘堰整治和小农水建设项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">721</span>个，占计划项目的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">140.5%</span>，其中完成当家塘堰整治<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">452</span>口、沟渠套洗<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">197</span>条、泵站维修（新建）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">69</span>处。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
