"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">副主席：谢先火<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">协管提案委员会、教科文卫委员会工作，联系官桥镇、高铁岭镇及党群口、宣传口政协联络处（组）工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">副主席：严嘉芬<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">分管社会和法制委员会、文史资料和学习委员会工作，联系牌洲湾镇、潘家湾镇及政法口、金融口、教育口政协联络处（组）工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">副主席：赵季明<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">分管经济人口资源环境委员会、港澳台侨和民族宗教委员会工作，联系鱼岳镇、新街镇及农业口、建设口政协联络处（组）工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">副主席：刘<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span>平<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">分管宣传、调研室、委员工作委员会、财务工作，联系渡普镇、陆溪镇及政府综合口、经贸口政协联络处（组）工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">秘书长：韩<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span>文<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 28pt; margin: 21.75pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">协助主席处理政协日常工作，负责政协机关目标责任制管理、委室协调、信息宣传工作，主持办公室工作。<