/span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个，三湖连江整体开发项目等旅游项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个，武深高速项目等城市交通项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个，文体会展中心项目等社会发展项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">目前，总投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">亿元的洁丽雅嘉鱼产业园项目已落户县经济开发区，正在加紧建设</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万锭高档毛巾特种纱和年产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1.5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">万吨高档毛巾现代化生产线。基地建成后，将年新增工业产值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">亿元，提供就业岗位</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个左右。届时将与该集团浙江总部、新疆品牌产业基地一起，在未来五年内，成为世界最大的毛巾生产企业。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据悉，我县实行县级领导联点重点项目制度，对重点项目建设进度实行一月一通报、半年一小结、全年结硬帐，推进签约项目早开工、开工项目早建成、建成项目早投产，形成策划一批、实施一批、建成一批的格局。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">同时，着力推进重点开工建设一批，确保洁丽雅集团嘉鱼产业园、中商伟博、汉方制药、大连成达等一批已签项目在上半年全面启动建设；重点建成投产一批，确保华亿通橡胶产业园、永幸管业、嘉能热电二期、比伦纸业、盛宇染织三期、怡和亚太、金桦实业、中科科凌、恒瑞化工等一批在建项目上半年如期投产；重点发展壮大一批，大力支持联乐工业园、卓尔纺织、中能锂电、武汉新联大、莱福特生物、天洋塑木等现有企业全面发展壮大，全年新建成投产项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">个以上。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">为加快项目建设，我县进一步完善了招商机制和优惠政策，加大了招商引资奖励力度，成立了工业、农业、旅游、城建商贸四个招商工作专班，积极营造宽松和谐的发展环境，全面推进重点项目建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></font></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1318','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-20/c414bed0992845f55c3deeeb2b2a574f.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">参观中能锂电<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"18\\\\\" month=\\\\\"2\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>日</st1:chsdate>，咸宁市委党校常务副校长王胜弘一行来我县就换届以来的工作进行调研，县委副书记李国光，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明陪同调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">王胜弘一行先后来到湖北中能锂电有限公司、华亿通橡胶产业园、湖北峰华科技有限公司，深入各企业的生产车间，与企业负责人亲切交流，询问企业的生产状况和面临的困难。在随后召开的座谈会上，王胜弘指出，在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年集中换届中，嘉鱼县领导重视、程序规范、创新有序、氛围和谐、成效明显，这次来主要就是调查摸底，实地感受嘉鱼换届中涌现出的好经验、好办法、好风貌，并把调研结果以书面材料的形式上报市委、市政府。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">李国光汇报了嘉鱼县换届以来的有关工作，他说，新一届的党委、政府班子与<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2006</span>年换届后情况相比，主要呈现了以下几个变化：年龄结构更趋合理，党政领导班子平均年龄从<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">43.1</span>降到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">41.6</span>岁；组成结构有所改善，更加注重女干部和党外干部培养；学历结构更加均衡，平均学历更高；岗位职责更加明确，县级班子中设置了专职人大主任，党政交叉任职从<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>名减少到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>名；镇级班子中，实行了书记、镇长分设，明确了党、政职责。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">座谈会上，县委党校、公务员局、陆溪镇、潘家湾镇等单位主要负责人汇报了换届以来的工作。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-20/638af5e473b9ddbbd03fe72739afdf89.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">会议现场</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1319','6','张姝、龙光辉','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-20/7aa7a90ba4dd3305ca29dbebbad923e4.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇、余珂正在栽种油茶苗<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-20/cca286f8b02cef24b4222a8786afa4d3.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">植树活动现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">春风化雨润无声，植树造林正当时。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，熊征宇、余珂等县四大家领导带领</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余名县直机关干部，来到嘉鱼县官桥镇阴山村油茶基地开展义务植树活动，拉开了我县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度全民植树造林的序幕。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">虽然天空飘着小雨，但是却难以湮灭大家劳动的热情。油茶栽植现场，人头攒动，彩旗飘扬。干部职工们纷纷来到各自的&ldquo;责任地&rdquo;，松土、扶苗、回填、压实、浇水，每个环节都一丝不苟，确保每株树苗都能茁壮成长。在大家齐心协力努力下，不一会儿，一棵棵翠绿的油茶苗就挺立山坡，为南嘉大地平添片片新绿。据统计，当天共</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">完成绿化面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">今年是我国开展全民义务植树活动</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">周年。据县林业局负责人介绍，为做大做强油茶产业，县委、县政府将发展油茶作为丘陵山区今后一段时期林业工作重点，并计划</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年内发展</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万亩油茶基地。据统计，近年来，我县每年义务植树达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">98</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万株，目前全县森林覆盖率达到了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">26.8%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2010</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年还获得了&ldquo;全国绿化模范县&rdquo;的荣誉称号。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1320','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-20/1cd9fe2213104a538f1c74e05368cd6f.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">黄光耀一行</font>在峰华科技参观指导</span>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" month=\\\\\"2\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日</st1:chsdate>，省发改委党组成员、纪检书记黄光耀一行来我县检查指导&ldquo;委县合作&rdquo;相关工作。县领导熊征宇、余珂、李国光、李鹏谋、葛婷、魏朝东、熊武华、吴维明，县委办主任章斌陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">黄光耀一行先后走访了官桥村油茶基地、中能锂电、峰华科技、华亿通橡胶产业园，并与企业负责人进行了深入交流。他说，嘉鱼区位优势明显，经济社会发展态势良好，特别是近年来省发改委与嘉鱼县进行&ldquo;委县合作&rdquo;取得了显著成效。他希望嘉鱼新一届领导班子将&ldquo;委县合作&rdquo;持续开展下去，进一步拓展投融资渠道，加大对保障性住房、供水管网建设、安全饮水工程，以及教育、卫生等基本公共服务支持力度，充分发挥已到位项目的效益和作用，切实把好事办好。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇在致辞中说，近年来，在省委、省政府的正确领导和省发改委的大力支持下，我县依托&ldquo;委县合作&rdquo;平台，借势发力，深入推进&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;建设，大力发展现代农业，科学开发旅游资源，全力夯实城乡基础，促进了县域经济的快速发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年，全县生产总值首次突破百亿元大关、达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">131.2</span>亿元，完成地方一般预算收入<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4.4</span>亿元，规模工业增加值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70.5</span>亿元，全社会固定资产投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">88.2</span>亿元。与<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2008</span>年相比，主要经济指标均实现了翻番目标。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">熊征宇表示，自<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2009</span>年搭建&ldquo;委县合作&rdquo;平台以来，省发改委领导多次亲临嘉鱼实地调研指导工作，在政策、项目、资金上给予我县极大的支持。新的一年寄托新的希望，新的目标谱写新的篇章。嘉鱼新一轮跨越式发展，需要省发改委一如既往地关注关爱、关心支持，需要各位领导一如既往地献计献策、传经送宝。在新的一年里，我县将进一步用活、用好&ldquo;委县合作&rdquo;这个平台，以更加饱满的工作热情、更加奋发的工作姿态、更加务实的工作作风，抢抓新机遇，迎接新挑战，再创新业绩，力争早日把嘉鱼建成湖北经济强县、长江临港新城。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂就三年来&ldquo;委县合作&rdquo;工作及嘉鱼县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年拟向上争取项目情况作了汇报。近年来，在项目争取上，省发改委大力支持帮助我县争取上级补助资金（项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">167</span>个，中央投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">47040.5</span>万元）；在政策扶持上，结合我县&ldquo;整村推进&rdquo;计划，整合资源统筹规划，开展&ldquo;迁村腾地&rdquo;，增加农村土地收益；在结对帮扶上，将官桥村选为&ldquo;城乡互联，结对共建&rdquo;联系帮扶村，有力地支持了该村整村推进新农村建设。同时，武深高速嘉鱼段、咸潘一级公路将在今年全面开工建设，嘉鱼长江大桥也有望在今年获立项审批。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<div><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p><o:p></o:p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-20/8c050056a39c5ce50350d0540f110be6.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1321','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/7eb3140ba0979ee9e77edd27716efb35.jpg\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">协调会现场</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" month=\\\\\"2\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日下午</st1:chsdate>，县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记、县长余珂，县委副书记李国光，副县长许隆高一行，来到洁丽雅二期施工建设现场，就项目建设、征地拆迁、还建安置等情况进行调研，并召开了项目建设协调会。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">在实地察看项目进展情况并听取了洁丽雅集团及县直相关部门负责人的情况汇报后，县委书记熊征宇指出，洁丽雅二期是县委县政府高度重视的重点项目，对县经济开发区新一轮发展具有重要意义。各相关部门要明确任务，全力支持配合项目推进，要搞好协调，主动帮助解决项目推进中出现的新情况新问题，举全县各方之力确保项目快速、顺利推进。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">在项目建设方面，熊征宇要求，鱼岳镇要加快进行还建安置点的建设，并尽快完成项目区内房屋拆迁和补偿安置工作；规划部门要做好还建安置点的规划方案；国土部门要协助完成土地证办理及土方测量工作；城投公司要配合建设引水管道和排污管道；县开发区、经信局、住建局、公安局等部门要做好项目推进过程中的各项协调工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂指出，今年是&ldquo;项目建设年&rdquo;，各级各部门必须牢固树立大抓项目、抓大项目的理念，加大力度，加快进度，集中人员、设备等各方力量，抢抓时间，倒排工期，努力使该项目早日建成投产。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">县委副书记李国光就下一阶段工作任务进行了部署。副县长许隆高介绍了该项目前期工作进展情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">县委办主任章斌、县政府办主任余忠东，县直相关部门负责人参加协调会。与会的县直相关部门负责人就如何更好发挥各自职能作了表态发言。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1322','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/63a7e64f3639c80f365f7723e532d330.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日晚，嘉鱼县召开嘉鱼大道、海航、长鹿农庄项目协调会。县领导熊征宇、余珂、葛婷、李新华、李电波、李德炳、魏萍、雷家兴、赵季明、刘平参加会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇指出，今年是&ldquo;项目建设年&rdquo;，各级各部门要一切为了项目转、要把项目建设作为一切工作的重心。他说，嘉鱼大道、海航、长鹿农庄项目都是县委、县政府高度重视的重点项目，对嘉鱼经济发展具有重要意义。各相关部门要统一思想、提高认识，认识到这三个项目的重要性；要明确任务，搞好协调，全力支持配合项目推进，举全县之力确保项目快速、顺利推进。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在项目建设方面，熊征宇要求，鱼岳镇要加快进行还建安置点的建设，并尽快完成项目区内房屋拆迁和补偿安置工作；规划部门要尽快做好三个项目的规划方案；国土部门要协助完成土地证办理及土方测量工作；财政局要保证项目资金落实到位；城投公司要加快融资；各相关部门要做好项目推进过程中的各项协调工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂主持会议，他要求，各级各部门要紧紧围绕县委、县政府的要求，把工作做好、落实到位，要踏踏实实、稳扎稳打；要牢固树立大抓项目、抓大项目的理念，加大力度，加快进度，集中人员、设备等各种力量，加快项目的推进。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/1adae6f2cd815dc9aff4699128639a9a.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1323','6','董育雄、江开群、汪姝琴','荆楚网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/4d84b4a964b8c6d96088417c0ba2e5c2.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇 雷平摄</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">访谈背景：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">29</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，湖北省委、省政府召开&ldquo;喜迎十八大，争创新业绩&rdquo;电视电话会议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼召开嘉鱼县三级干部大会，提出建设&ldquo;经济强县、临港新城、旅游胜地、鱼米之乡、幸福家园&rdquo;的发展定位。嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇在接受荆楚网记者专访时说，要坚定信心，争先进位，在新的起点上奋力推进嘉鱼经济社会发展新跨越，为早日建成湖北经济强县、长江临港新城打下坚实的基础，以优异成绩向党的十八大献礼！</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/f9cd969547b3ced03ac40afa3aa1a2f4.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></font><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">全国文明县城&mdash;&mdash;嘉鱼 刘俊摄<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">荆楚网记者（以下简称记者）：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年嘉鱼县经济社会屡创佳绩，民生工程又有大手笔，能否请你简要介绍一下相关情况。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼县生产总值首次突破百亿元大关，完成规模工业增加值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">70.5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，净增规模企业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">22</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家；农民人均纯收入达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8095</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">元。作为全省</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个县市之一获评全国文明县城，作为咸宁唯一县（市）代表，分别在全省农村工作会议、全市经济工作会议上作经验交流，先后荣获全省农业农村工作先进单位、全省中小企业成长工程先进单位等一批省级荣誉。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">全年新增蔬菜板块基地面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万亩，建成</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩现代设施农业基地，嘉鱼县无公害农产品认证达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">175</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个。深入推进&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;建设，全年建成投产项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，新增工业税收近</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元。成功引进海航集团、广东长鹿集团开发我县旅游资源，山湖温泉与咸宁温泉整体组合当选&ldquo;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">灵秀湖北十大旅游名片&rdquo;，官桥镇被确定为湖北省第二批&ldquo;旅游名镇&rdquo;创建单位。城市经济发展迅速，投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3380</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元新建的环湖公园已投入使用。结合&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，加快推进农田水利基本建设，全年完成投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2.8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元。以土地整治项目为载体，实施官桥村、净堡村、四邑村、界石村等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个村迁村腾地、整村推进新农村试点工程。新组建了南嘉中学，启动了投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元的县文体会展中心建设，投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1.2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元进行县人民医院整体迁建工程。加强干部作风建设，大力推行行政审批&ldquo;两集中、两到位&rdquo;，深入开展治庸问责工作，各级各部门党员干部服务发展意识明显增强。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">记者：省委、省政府召开&ldquo;喜迎十八大，争创新业绩&rdquo;电视电话会议，也吹响了全省凝神聚力、以&ldquo;五进&rdquo;精神落实中央&ldquo;稳中求进&rdquo;要求的&ldquo;集结号&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼县委、县政府经济社会发展的总体思路和目标是什么？实现既定的思路和目标，坚持的方向是什么？</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年是实施&ldquo;十二五&rdquo;规划承上启下的关键一年，是喜迎十八大召开的重要一年，也是贯彻县第十三次党代会精神的开局之年。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，县委、县政府将按照&ldquo;一个迈大步&rdquo;、&ldquo;两个上水平&rdquo;、&ldquo;三个新突破&rdquo;的发展思路，全面推进大园区、大城建、大旅游、大交通和新农村&ldquo;四大一新&rdquo;发展战略，即推动工业发展迈大步，确保农业和第三产业发展上水平，在城乡建设、交通建设和社会事业发展上取得新突破。力争实现嘉鱼县生产总值同比增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">18%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，规模工业增加值增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，城镇居民人均可支配收入、农民人均纯收入分别增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，万元生产总值综合能耗下降</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，城镇新增就业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人。实现既定目标，主要坚持&ldquo;四个第一&rdquo;，即始终坚持工业第一战略，始终坚持项目第一抓手，始终坚持民生第一追求，始终坚持维稳第一责任，时刻保持争先进位的紧迫感和使命感，用科学的方法、开阔的思路破解难题，勇于突破常规，敢于闯出新路，以超常的创新举措带动诸多瓶颈要素的全面突破，把优势做得更优，把劣势逐渐扭转，用每一年的新跨越，实现进军&ldquo;第一方阵&rdquo;的大跨越。</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/1557890a9df50a77fe8bd1014d41a1f6.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: #f7fcff; margin: 11.25pt 0cm; line-height: 17.25pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">临港新城正在崛起 张大乐摄<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">记者：今年嘉鱼县在发展县域经济方面将有哪些重大举措？能否介绍一下今年的重点项目建设情况</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">?</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年既是建设湖北经济强县打基础的一年，也是加快推进跨越式发展的攻坚之年。嘉鱼要抢抓全省&ldquo;两圈一带&rdquo;、长江中游城市群、咸嘉新城建设等一系列重大战略机遇，充分发挥农业、工业、旅游、交通、环境良好的基础条件，重点在建设经济强县、建设临港新城、建设旅游胜地、建设鱼米之乡、建设幸福嘉鱼等五个方面下功夫，发挥农业特色优势，继续推进一区多园建设，加快对接咸嘉新城，全力推进海航集团、长鹿农庄等重大旅游项目建设，挖掘生态、文化资源，打响&ldquo;诗经嘉鱼</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">?</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">二乔故里&rdquo;品牌，全力打造实力新嘉鱼、活力新嘉鱼、魅力新嘉鱼、合力新嘉鱼。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在县第十三次党代会上，新一届县委提出了建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的新目标，力争五年内实现&ldquo;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">33221</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&rdquo;的奋斗目标，即嘉鱼县生产总值达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，规模工业企业超过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家；财政总收入达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，年税收过千万元企业超过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家；全社会固定资产投资五年累计完成</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元。年初，通过四大家联席会议，把工业、农业、城建、旅游等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重点项目全部责任到人，成立</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重点项目建设指挥部，以及嘉鱼长江大桥、武汉新港嘉鱼港区、武深高速嘉鱼段、咸嘉新城等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重大项目前期工作推进领导小组，强力推进项目建设，力争在一季度海航集团、长鹿农庄项目完成一期土地征用，正式签订房屋拆迁安置协议并启动拆迁，县城三环线官桥至石矶头段完成征地拆迁工作，洁丽雅集团嘉鱼产业基地、大连成达、县文体会展中心、武嘉一级公路绿化配套工程全面开工建设，经济开发区二期、嘉鱼大道加快建设。</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/496777a18d3ea381fe24f5e0e375e03e.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: #f7fcff; margin: 11.25pt 0cm; line-height: 17.25pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">过亿项目纷纷在嘉鱼建成投产 刘俊摄<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">记者：如何实现嘉鱼县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年经济社会发展和&ldquo;喜迎十八大，争创新业绩&rdquo;主题实践活动目标呢？通过哪些活动载体来确保活动实效？</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇：根据省委、市委的要求，结合我县实际，县委研究制定了具体的《实施方案》，确立以</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">项活动为载体，迅速掀起主题实践活动热潮。嘉鱼县各级党组织和广大党员干部对照活动《实施方案》的要求，联系工作实际，做到&ldquo;四个结合&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">一是与提振精神区位相结合。把这次主题实践活动作为加强党的建设的重要抓手，深入开展&ldquo;学党史、知党情、跟党走&rdquo;学习教育活动，组织嘉鱼县党员干部学习党的历史，增强党性意识、忧患意识、责任意识和大局意识，进一步坚定加快把嘉鱼建设成为人人向往之地的信心和决心。扎实开展&ldquo;基层组织建设年&rdquo;活动，真正使嘉鱼县党的基层组织建起来、用起来、活起来、强起来。结合&ldquo;双联双促&rdquo;活动，不断巩固和扩大&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动、&ldquo;城乡互联、百村共建、千户帮扶&rdquo;等活动成果，真正做到问政于民、问计于民、问需于民，切实知民情、聚民智、惠民生。认真组织好创先争优活动专项表彰，树立一批身边的先进典型，形成比、学、赶、超的浓厚氛围，提振精神区位，营造&ldquo;嘉鱼气场&rdquo;，为推动我县科学发展、跨越式发展提供强大政治动力和精神动力。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">二是与深入解放思想相结合。解放思想是跨越式发展的&ldquo;发动机&rdquo;，是第一动力。当前，人才青黄不接，工业发展与环保矛盾日益突出。对于这些问题，我们解放思想，坚持用市场的办法、改革的办法、开放的办法，来加以解决；结合主题实践活动，不断创新项目建设、社会管理等机制，实施人才强县工程，破解发展中的一系列难题。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">三是与优化投资环境相结合。结合主题实践活动，紧紧围绕打造全市乃至全省最优投资环境这一目标，扎实开展&ldquo;五亮五比五创&rdquo;活动，坚持以评选&ldquo;十佳&rdquo;示范窗口、&ldquo;十佳&rdquo;服务行业为切入点，突出抓好窗口单位和服务行业创先争优活动，把&ldquo;五亮五比五创&rdquo;活动不断引向深入。巩固和深化治庸问责工作成果，在嘉鱼县各级机关中开展&ldquo;三抓一促&rdquo;活动，切实转变机关作风，打造学习型、创新型、服务型、效能型、节约型、廉洁型机关。大力倡导开短会、讲短话、发短文、简办事，落实&ldquo;四减五制三集中&rdquo;公开承诺，即减审批事项、审批环节、审批时限、审批费用，推行窗口受理制、首问负责制、一次告知制、限时办结制、责任追究制，集中审批职能、审批事项、审批人员，营造和谐发展氛围，不断优化我县投资软环境。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">四是与狠抓工作落实相结合。今年是全省&ldquo;工作落实年&rdquo;，按照省委、省政府的要求，结合主题实践活动，突出重点抓落实，大力开展&ldquo;重大项目建设年&rdquo;活动，树立&ldquo;想方设法争项目、千方百计引项目、优化服务建项目&rdquo;的工作理念，围绕年初确定的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重点项目和政府</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">件实事，努力形成策划一批、实施一批、建成一批的格局，助推县域经济跨越发展。同时，充分发挥综合考评的&ldquo;指挥棒&rdquo;作用，促各项工作落实。</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/224ae28bbac938ba7af00ae29c1f1152.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: #f7fcff; margin: 11.25pt 0cm; line-height: 17.25pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">农业生产喜获丰收 张大乐摄<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">记者：今年嘉鱼县在改善民生方面还将有哪些动作？</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇：我们将从四个方面改善民生、顺应民盼，大力发展社会事业，不断提高人民幸福指数。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">一是大力推进文化大发展大繁荣。重点抓好县文化馆、图书馆、镇综合文化站等公益文化场所免费开放工作；组织开展社区演出、文化下乡下村、主题广场晚会、城乡文艺汇演等各类文体活动；创作一台反映嘉鱼地方特色的文艺节目，争取承办一次省级体育比赛活动，规划建设一个文化产业园。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">二是大力发展科教卫生事业。不断加大对科技的投入，力争培育中国名牌产品</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个、湖北名牌</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1-2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，努力争创全国科技先进县。进一步完善教育经费保障机制，在城区新建</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1-2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">所公立幼儿园、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">所特殊学校，支持县一中争创省级示范高中。深入推进医药卫生体制改革，全面实施镇卫生院、村卫生室标准化建设，努力促进基本公共卫生服务均等化。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">三是大力提高社会保障水平。建立完善劳资管理制度，促进城乡劳动力和谐就业。完善被征地农民社会保障政策，全面启动新型农村社会养老保险。健全困难群众临时救助制度，加强扶贫开发、移民后扶工作，加快还建房和保障性住房建设，不断提高城乡居民保障水平。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">四是大力保护生态环境。认真抓好节能减排工作，加大环境保护执法力度，对新上项目严格控制增量，严把环评审批准入关，引导企业发展循环经济，推行清洁生产。加大饮用水源地保护力度，促进经济和生态协调发展。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">五是大力创新社会管理。坚持用群众工作统揽信访工作，进一步畅通群众诉求渠道，完善社会矛盾调解化解机制。加快构建公共安全体系，严格食品药品安全监管，提高公共事件应急处置能力，防范重特大事故发生。深入开展平安嘉鱼创建活动，不断夯实综治基层基础，推进社区（村）规范化建设。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-21/6a68a939eafbc50dd25e45a8a7bca4ab.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: #f7fcff; margin: 11.25pt 0cm; line-height: 17.25pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">元宵灯会花灯迷人眼 刘俊摄、</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: #f7fcff; margin: 11.25pt 0cm; line-height: 17.25pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"background: #f7fcff; margin: 11.25pt 0cm; line-height: 17.25pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");

